{
  "stem": "5551.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was too young to be able to judge the situation, but my parents soon knew that it is time to get away from Germany.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so in 1934-- that is, to put it in perspective, a year and a half after the Nazi takeover, which occurred in January of 1933-- we left [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Germany to join our family in the east, that is to say, in Poland.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we settled in a border town, Katowice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is when my brother and I started learning Polish.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we were later enrolled in a Jewish high school-- it was known as gymnasium-- that was prestigious.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "By the name of-- it carried the name of Firstenburg in Bendzin.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This was a Jewish gymnasium of high-quality education that included Jewish and Hebrew education, a kind of preparation for the Zionist dream of eventually going to what was then Palestine.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It is there where I learned Hebrew.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "People often ask me whether I lived in Israel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I spoke Hebrew before there was an Israel.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I actually, much to my regret, never did live in Israel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Still, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] our goal was to go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But in those days, the admission of Jews to Palestine was limited to capitalists, people with financial resources.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I don't remember exactly what the requirements were, but I know that we could not meet them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Merchant.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Fairly well is the correct description.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were not rich, but we were not poor.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we lived on a fair standard.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That school cost money, but to my parents, no price was too high for the children's education.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "If there was money to be saved, it would have been saved on anything else but on the children's education.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Exactly.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
